; Btw (TODO): I think for the registry command there are all modifiers available as for the normal section since the command is actually handled like a section.
Registry loadUnicodeTextFile("") /regedit /Sysnative
; Btw (TODO): Special treatment of command does not breaks highlighting if quote in loadUnicodeTextFile is missing.
Registry loadUnicodeTextFile(') /regedit


